{"tid":1700991,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登巴斯改變社會： \"小雨天\"食店 由全日TVB新聞台，今日轉播VIUTV！","createTime":"2019-11-08T19:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T23:51:47.000Z","uid":280192,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6d61e40cafbb07052406f70a950233cc17419969","tid":1700991,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"話說上個POST日前出，裡面舉例鬧<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣&quot;小雨天&quot;全日播TVB新聞台影響細路</span>，並鼓勵黃店都播片：<br />\n<br />\n黃店只要再升級到播片潮，呢場運動就等於永續左，只係等贏！<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1697362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1697362/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n全靠巴絲，事隔一日個post上左熱門，唔知係咪小雨天老細有睇連登，<span style=\"color: red;\">今日改播VIUTV</span>！旁邊飯小館可能係同老細，一齊轉左！<br />\n<br />\n播<span style=\"color: red;\">TVB新聞台</span>變VIUTV簡直功德無量。以儆效尤，好值得青試食，輕輕懲罰一下。大家亦可去openrice等細細力表揚。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果呢類鋪生意好左，相信各區改變陸續有來。</span><br />\n<br />\nPS. 呢間店我所知無表明過立場(入面D阿姐感覺譚仔)。無所謂扮黃扮藍。手足如堅持非黃不食，十分尊重，同時致以萬分敬意。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 宜家返工經過，由TVB陣爛臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，變左VIUTV嘅清香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，身心都舒暢返少少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvRteoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvRteoC.jpg&h=7b690a6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bbf52c9cb25a81f4ced07bb46668cafffb9aafb","tid":1700991,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:14:08.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3